  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Normal fasting blood glucose, BMI 19-25 kg/m2, for women: hormon based contraceptives

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  gastrointestinal diseases or food allergies e.g. lactose-, gluten intolerance,
             metabolic disorders e.g. diabetes, tobacco/snuff users. Antibiotic or probiotic usage
             within two weeks, and during the study. Vegetarians
      </textblock>
